    "causal_summary": "REJECTED 2026-05-13 after six-hypothesis perf investigation (H1-H6). Opt-in ONNX Runtime backend shipped initially but measured 3.5x slower than sbert/PyTorch+MPS at parity-preserving settings on Apple Silicon. H1 found CoreML EP only claims 23% of Gemma ops; Neural Engine barely active. H3 found static-pad128 unlocks fast inference (40.9ms p50) but breaks parity (mean cosine 0.869). Production code reverted; packet retained as decision record. See decision-record.md.",
